command -v nvm


You can list available versions using ls-remote:

nvm ls-remote


To install a specific version of node:

nvm install 14.7.0 # or 16.3.0, 12.22.1, etc
nvm use version
instalar ultima lts con

nvm install --lts
nvm use --lts
